organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jimmie Johnson gave Hendrick Motorsports its first Nascar Sprint Cup victory of the season by winning Saturday in the Subway Fresh Fit 500 at Phoenix International Speedway.
